{"tid":1431793,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「光復香港，時代革命」⋯⋯⋯","createTime":"2019-08-08T05:31:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-08T06:00:16.000Z","uid":279238,"like":6,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"3e780b3d8cebccd5ea0d3c8a3dbbe806d301547a","tid":1431793,"uid":279238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T05:31:15.000Z","msg":"既然和理非吹風覺得「光復香港，時代革命」咁有問題，或者咁難理解，咁不如就以依兩句做基礎，再後面加多兩句，去令啲和理非明白，只有眼前路，沒有身後身<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">「光復香港，時代革命，重奪主權，港人治港」</span></span><br />\n<br />\n我知港人治港好9up，但有腦嘅人都知依家係京人治港，西環治港，如果打出依個旗號，對家/潔癖和理非應該無咁多口實<br />\n<br />\n利申：「光復香港，時代革命」每次夢遊都叫到喉沙<br />\n<br />\n以下開放討論，希望各高手提供意見，得到新共識"},{"pid":"fb1b6925f98d27814fd7dc62fbdf01cdf4873711","tid":1431793,"uid":279238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T05:32:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8e305d3c942581d0db203975b4b8dcec774fffcb","tid":1431793,"uid":279238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T05:33:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"54ff742b337127f927580567c49f7dd6c9bcfcbe","tid":1431793,"uid":178228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T05:33:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我地<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">群龍皆首 群龍無首</span></span></blockquote>"},{"pid":"a3983ae9404af6efcdf34429a1ff293703923ee2","tid":1431793,"uid":231909,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T05:33:22.000Z","msg":"借個位,提提你<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BmepMAH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBmepMAH.jpg&h=aab03643&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xp7KMz5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fxp7KMz5.png&h=1dddb453&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>出黎嬴翻香港</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"a48537e76eb5ce05df37c8b4beca11e50893f5b4","tid":1431793